Package org.asl.socketserver

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Servable
    Interface for games that read and write across streams.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractGame
    Base class for games.
    BestScore
    Plain old Java object that associates a numeric score (integer) with the player who set the score.
    Dictionary
    Library that provides methods for retrieving words from a word source.
    GameServer
    Accepts incoming network connection requests and dispatches them onto parallel game threads.
    GameThread
    Manages the connection with a remote machine for the lifetime of the thread.
    GameTracker
    Locates servable classes within the project directory structure.
